      1165,
      893
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Ta có $f'(t) = 0 \\Rightarrow -2000t^2 + 10000 = 0 \\Leftrightarrow t^2 = 5 \\Leftrightarrow t = \\sqrt{5}$ (do $t \\ge 0$)."
  },
  {
